705573f-c.title: Brooklyn: Marcy Avenue - Lynch Street
705573f-c.text:
Marcy Avenue, north from Lynch Street, showing
W. P. A. track removal operations. The buildings
nre on the west side of the avenue. View 2 is north
from Heyward Avenue, and view 8 is north from Rutledge
Street. Lynch Avenue, Heyward Avenue, and Rutledge
Street follow each other consecutively from south to
north.
June 24, 1936
Views 1,2,3
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
CREDIT LNE IIPERATIVE
